Class LowerCaseIdServicesDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.idm.IdServicesDecorator
      • org.forgerock.openam.idm.LowerCaseIdServicesDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdServices

    public class LowerCaseIdServicesDecorator
extends IdServicesDecorator
    Implementation of the IdServices interface that just ensures all attribute names are lower case to ensure API consistency.
    Since:
    12.0.0
    See Also:
    OPENAM-3159
